          <div class = "text"> <h1 style = "font-family: 'Courier New', Courier, monospace; font-size: 30px;"> Saudi Arabia Grand Prix </h1>
             
              <P>The race was started at 20:00 AST on 27 March and lasted for 50 laps. </p>
               <P>Red Bull's Max Verstappen won the race ahead of Ferrari's Charles Leclerc, who set the fastest lap for an additional poin</p>
                 <P>Leclerc and Verstappen started a DRS battle in which at turn 27 neither driver wanted to take the lead and be vulnerable to a DRS attack in the straight to turn 1.
                 </P>
                 <p>Verstappen took a full lap lead by lap 46 and  Yellow flags on turn 1 after the Albon–Stroll incident precluded Leclerc for a DRS offensive on lap 48 </p>
                 <P> This therefore lead to Verstappen winning the race </P> 
                 <P> Charles Leclerc had the fastest lap at time: 1:31.634 on lap 48.</P>
